 Torontonians (designers\, coders\, urban planners\, government staff\, map
 pers\, policy-makers\, students\, communications strategists\, community o
 rganizers\, and more) who share an interest in making Toronto more respons
 ive\, prosperous\, sustainable\, and equitable through design\, tech\, and
